1
00:00:04,279 --> 00:00:06,239
(Previously)
At first, I didn't think I'd like it.

2
00:00:07,965 --> 00:00:10,085
But the more I looked at
it, the more I fell in love.

3
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:13,084
And I think I'll love it
even more in the future.

4
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:20,920
Let's make this place our home.

5
00:00:21,462 --> 00:00:22,489
Our home.

6
00:00:30,439 --> 00:00:31,917
Of course you're going to love it.

7
00:00:32,461 --> 00:00:34,357
Our home is called ChermChey.

8
00:00:37,719 --> 00:00:40,040
I made this for you.

9
00:00:41,174 --> 00:00:42,174
So you won't lose it.

10
00:00:44,883 --> 00:00:46,132
It's a Phra Khun Phaen amulet.

11
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:48,514
This one is super charming.

12
00:00:48,515 --> 00:00:50,349
Boom!

13
00:01:02,592 --> 00:01:03,624
What's up, Joi?

14
00:01:03,625 --> 00:01:04,811
Boss, P'Erng!

15
00:01:04,812 --> 00:01:08,012
Customers are fighting in front of the
shop. One of our tables is already broken!

16
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,050
Damn it!

17
00:01:11,911 --> 00:01:12,911
What's going on?

18
00:01:13,708 --> 00:01:14,708
Calm down.

19
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,040
Stay out of this!

20
00:01:17,176 --> 00:01:20,225
Go fight somewhere else!
Don't do this in my shop!

21
00:01:20,452 --> 00:01:21,452
I think...

22
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:24,754
They're trying to wreck
the place, not just fight.

23
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:47,640
Who is that?

24
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,226
Hey.

25
00:01:53,725 --> 00:01:55,669
Shit, how did In get here?

26
00:01:55,670 --> 00:01:57,517
How do you know who I am?

27
00:02:17,534 --> 00:02:20,000
Whoa, calm down, man!

28
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:21,954
I'm going to kill you!

29
00:02:22,271 --> 00:02:23,271
I'm sorry, man!

30
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,760
Who hired you?

31
00:02:31,536 --> 00:02:33,845
Mr... Mr...

32
00:02:34,253 --> 00:02:35,387
Mr. Who?

33
00:02:35,388 --> 00:02:40,000
Mr. Aten! Aten hired us!

34
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:03,599
Erng, hang in there!

35
00:03:05,239 --> 00:03:08,200
Hurry, P'Erng! Let's go!

36
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,581
Hey, bro!

37
00:03:11,582 --> 00:03:12,203
Let go of me!

38
00:03:12,204 --> 00:03:13,512
Bro!

39
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,115
Can't you see what's happening?

40
00:03:15,116 --> 00:03:18,400
Stop! Have you lost your mind?

41
00:03:18,646 --> 00:03:19,646
Erng!

42
00:03:20,271 --> 00:03:22,151
How can I calm down
when the place is on fire?!

43
00:03:22,409 --> 00:03:23,409
Hia!

44
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,890
Erng!

45
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:39,960
May this place be filled
with joy and warmth.

46
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:49,439
Three years ago, I opened
a small bar with my ex.

47
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:53,872
I poured my heart into it
until it became popular.

48
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,567
Then we decided to expand.

49
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:01,730
You can imagine how
much I loved that place.

50
00:04:04,269 --> 00:04:07,002
But then I caught him bringing
someone else into our bed.

51
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,774
Can I take over your bar?

52
00:04:11,635 --> 00:04:12,951
I want to start a business.

53
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,887
I've already thought of a name.

54
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,423
Really? Let's hear it.

55
00:04:27,414 --> 00:04:28,431
ChermChey.

56
00:04:30,841 --> 00:04:31,841
I'm Cherm.
(Out-dated)

57
00:04:32,667 --> 00:04:33,907
And you're Chey.
(Old-fashioned)

58
00:04:34,404 --> 00:04:35,405
Let's take a selfie.

59
00:04:38,851 --> 00:04:41,296
ChermChey is officially open!

60
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,798
At first, I didn't think I'd like it.

61
00:04:54,799 --> 00:04:57,388
But the more I looked at it,
the more I fell in love.

62
00:04:58,658 --> 00:05:00,618
And I think I'll love it
even more in the future.

63
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:04,122
Let's make this place our home.

64
00:05:04,621 --> 00:05:05,787
Our home.

65
00:06:20,919 --> 00:06:22,385
This notebook is ours.

66
00:06:24,652 --> 00:06:26,706
To write down all our memories together.

67
00:06:46,479 --> 00:06:48,150
What's this little girl's name?

68
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,959
She doesn't have a name yet.

69
00:06:52,685 --> 00:06:54,954
Can you name her for us?

70
00:06:56,179 --> 00:06:57,179
Earn.

71
00:06:58,397 --> 00:06:59,397
Her name is Earn Earn.

72
00:07:00,771 --> 00:07:02,349
A combination of In and Erng?

73
00:07:03,619 --> 00:07:04,324
Yeah.

74
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,078
That's so cute.

75
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:36,200
"Chermchey"
(Episode 8)

76
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,640
- Watch out!
- Whoa!

77
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,933
Hey, Hia!

78
00:09:36,883 --> 00:09:38,629
Why are you shouting?

79
00:09:40,317 --> 00:09:41,789
I know you're awake.

80
00:09:42,333 --> 00:09:43,333
You're just ignoring me.

81
00:09:45,711 --> 00:09:47,139
Ouch.

82
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,404
I'm depressed.

83
00:10:01,492 --> 00:10:03,132
I don't want to talk to anyone right now.

84
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,517
My heart is aching.

85
00:10:06,966 --> 00:10:08,398
Because of the fire?

86
00:10:10,892 --> 00:10:12,009
And last night...

87
00:10:13,097 --> 00:10:15,121
Where did you go when the shop was burning?

88
00:10:15,801 --> 00:10:17,293
I went to beat someone up.

89
00:10:18,699 --> 00:10:20,223
I saw it on the CCTV.

90
00:10:20,631 --> 00:10:23,121
Someone was lurking around the house.

91
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,958
So I went out to deal with him.

92
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,601
The guy who burned down our shop...

93
00:10:37,689 --> 00:10:40,312
is the same guy who
started the fight last month.

94
00:10:43,959 --> 00:10:46,039
But I couldn't do anything
to the guy who hired him.

95
00:10:46,515 --> 00:10:47,515
Who?

96
00:10:49,509 --> 00:10:50,952
Is it who you thought it was?

97
00:10:52,222 --> 00:10:53,446
It wasn't Bom.

98
00:10:55,305 --> 00:10:56,826
It was Aten.

99
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,672
Are you tired of me?

100
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:10,120
Tired of me causing all these problems?

101
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,779
Are you a soap opera actress?

102
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,563
Stop reading from a drama script.

103
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,320
Don't be stupid...

104
00:11:21,321 --> 00:11:23,297
and try to push me away
to find someone better.

105
00:11:23,886 --> 00:11:25,446
A "good person" and
the "person you love"...

106
00:11:25,447 --> 00:11:26,814
are not the same thing.

107
00:11:28,446 --> 00:11:29,393
And another thing...

108
00:11:29,394 --> 00:11:31,289
None of this is your fault, Erng.

109
00:11:32,332 --> 00:11:34,035
Aten is the crazy one.

110
00:11:34,806 --> 00:11:36,943
Stop acting like a victim in a drama.

111
00:11:38,303 --> 00:11:40,411
And go back to being
the annoying Erng I know.

112
00:11:42,406 --> 00:11:43,903
I'm never breaking up with you.

113
00:11:45,082 --> 00:11:46,082
Got it?

114
00:11:49,062 --> 00:11:50,892
I'm not breaking up with you either.

115
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:57,091
Can you stop scolding me?

116
00:11:58,542 --> 00:11:59,585
I get it now.

117
00:12:00,899 --> 00:12:02,872
Well, you were talking nonsense.

118
00:12:03,597 --> 00:12:04,597
I'm sorry.

119
00:12:04,998 --> 00:12:07,353
I really love your sassy mouth.

120
00:12:08,577 --> 00:12:10,049
If you hadn't just woken up...

121
00:12:11,455 --> 00:12:12,695
I would've devoured you by now.

122
00:12:13,546 --> 00:12:15,951
Save the devouring for later.

123
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,821
But as a devoted husband...

124
00:12:21,184 --> 00:12:22,829
how are you going to handle this?

125
00:12:31,768 --> 00:12:32,760
Do I look handsome today?

126
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,760
Yes.

127
00:12:34,763 --> 00:12:36,363
But what does that have to do with this?

128
00:12:40,596 --> 00:12:44,780
It does, because I dressed up to
meet P'On and my sister-in-law.

129
00:12:45,687 --> 00:12:47,767
Did Aten think he was the
only one with connections?

130
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:37,953
What the hell are you doing here?

131
00:13:39,449 --> 00:13:42,163
I came to apologize to P'Erng and to you.

132
00:13:43,342 --> 00:13:45,346
I didn't know you were
Araya's younger brother.

133
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,578
What happened to your face?

134
00:13:49,819 --> 00:13:53,955
My dad beat me. Araya
made one call to his secretary...

135
00:13:54,953 --> 00:13:56,555
and my dad dragged me back home.

136
00:13:57,825 --> 00:14:00,992
He was furious that I
burned down your shop.

137
00:14:02,352 --> 00:14:04,626
I don't actually feel that guilty, though.

138
00:14:05,171 --> 00:14:06,811
I'm just apologizing to get it over with.

139
00:14:08,973 --> 00:14:10,740
Then you deserved...

140
00:14:11,375 --> 00:14:12,898
getting beaten up.

141
00:14:14,394 --> 00:14:15,834
I'm going in to apologize to P'Erng.

142
00:14:16,364 --> 00:14:18,284
I don't want my dad to beat me again...

143
00:14:18,285 --> 00:14:19,864
for dragging my feet.

144
00:14:20,816 --> 00:14:21,938
I heard everything.

145
00:14:26,472 --> 00:14:28,307
Consider your apology accepted.

146
00:14:29,123 --> 00:14:30,234
Now, get out.

147
00:14:32,003 --> 00:14:34,078
Can I stay in your room for a bit longer?

148
00:14:34,079 --> 00:14:36,837
I don't want my dad's men
reporting that I'm insincere.

149
00:14:38,923 --> 00:14:40,914
But you aren't sincere anyway.

150
00:14:41,957 --> 00:14:43,067
Seriously...

151
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,929
why the hell did you do all this?

152
00:14:47,607 --> 00:14:48,607
For the thrill, I guess.

153
00:14:49,166 --> 00:14:50,310
Just for the thrill?

154
00:14:51,398 --> 00:14:53,195
I really want to slap you, Aten.

155
00:14:54,011 --> 00:14:56,067
You took everything from me.

156
00:14:57,246 --> 00:14:58,326
You wanted Bom...

157
00:14:58,870 --> 00:15:00,649
and he packed his bags to be with you.

158
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,936
What more do you want from me?

159
00:15:04,795 --> 00:15:07,750
Is being this malicious
just who you really are?

160
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,171
Where did the sweet kid
I used to care about go?

161
00:15:12,172 --> 00:15:13,710
Ever since P'Bom broke up with you...

162
00:15:14,299 --> 00:15:16,138
he hasn't been the same with me.

163
00:15:19,539 --> 00:15:20,860
Why, P'Erng?

164
00:15:20,861 --> 00:15:23,138
Even though P'Bom chose me...

165
00:15:24,317 --> 00:15:25,935
why did it turn out like this?

166
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:28,669
Even though I'm his official partner...

167
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:30,397
he never respects me!

168
00:15:30,398 --> 00:15:31,786
That's between you and him.

169
00:15:31,787 --> 00:15:33,221
It has nothing to do with me.

170
00:15:33,810 --> 00:15:36,133
Stop dragging me into your mess.

171
00:15:36,134 --> 00:15:38,277
It does. I was jealous of you.

172
00:15:38,458 --> 00:15:40,687
The happier you were, the more I hated it.

173
00:15:44,496 --> 00:15:46,855
Did destroying me actually make you happy?

174
00:15:47,807 --> 00:15:49,146
Or...

175
00:15:50,234 --> 00:15:51,234
are you hurting too?

176
00:15:58,896 --> 00:16:02,561
You need to ask yourself
what you're really feeling.

177
00:16:03,468 --> 00:16:06,986
Of course I'm happy. I
stole P'Bom from you.

178
00:16:07,575 --> 00:16:08,822
It felt amazing.

179
00:16:11,361 --> 00:16:14,632
People who are actually
happy don't act like this.

180
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,233
The Aten I knew...

181
00:16:21,732 --> 00:16:22,899
wasn't like this.

182
00:16:35,731 --> 00:16:37,048
I'm not mad at you about Bom.

183
00:16:37,773 --> 00:16:40,844
But about the shop, I'm absolutely furious.

184
00:16:44,653 --> 00:16:46,259
So apologize to me, you little brat.

185
00:16:47,574 --> 00:16:51,176
After what I did, you
still call me your brother?

186
00:16:52,174 --> 00:16:54,342
If we can get mad, we can forgive too.

187
00:16:57,924 --> 00:16:59,773
I'm too awful for anyone to forgive.

188
00:17:01,768 --> 00:17:03,031
I forgive you.

189
00:17:06,205 --> 00:17:07,673
And so does Nok.

190
00:17:08,943 --> 00:17:10,924
Everyone goes through a dark phase.

191
00:17:10,925 --> 00:17:12,684
Let bygones be bygones.

192
00:17:12,685 --> 00:17:14,642
If you know you did wrong...

193
00:17:14,643 --> 00:17:16,102
just start over.

194
00:17:18,142 --> 00:17:20,252
You don't have to hate yourself so much.

195
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:25,352
If you've learned your
lesson, you're still my brother.

196
00:17:27,347 --> 00:17:29,307
And about Bom, you
weren't the only one at fault.

197
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:33,207
It takes two to tango.

198
00:17:33,208 --> 00:17:36,351
I'm the only one who did nothing wrong.

199
00:17:36,804 --> 00:17:39,357
I'm the innocent princess in all of this.

200
00:17:41,352 --> 00:17:44,597
You say you're not mad, but
you punched P'Bom's face in.

201
00:17:44,598 --> 00:17:45,991
Well, I was mad back then.

202
00:17:46,263 --> 00:17:47,934
But I'm not mad anymore.

203
00:17:47,935 --> 00:17:49,021
And what about you?

204
00:17:49,656 --> 00:17:52,372
You love each other, but you
threw a wrench at his head?

205
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:55,424
I love him, but I was mad too.

206
00:17:55,651 --> 00:17:57,651
Do you know how hard it
was for us to be together?

207
00:17:59,751 --> 00:18:01,384
Then you have to take good care of him.

208
00:18:02,109 --> 00:18:06,246
Wow, that's sharp. Who's both
beautiful and kind? Me, of course.

209
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:09,845
Are we good now, P'Erng?

210
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,535
Fix my shop first, then we'll be good.

211
00:18:12,536 --> 00:18:16,426
Sure, I was planning
to fix it for you anyway.

212
00:18:16,427 --> 00:18:21,123
So, we're good now, right?

213
00:18:21,124 --> 00:18:25,200
Yeah, fine. But why did
your dad beat you so hard?

214
00:18:25,699 --> 00:18:30,104
He wants me to break up with P'Bom
and to send me to study abroad.

215
00:18:30,603 --> 00:18:32,307
I said I wouldn't go, so he beat me up.

216
00:18:33,849 --> 00:18:35,641
I have a favor to ask.

217
00:18:37,001 --> 00:18:39,425
Can you take me to see P'Bom?

218
00:18:40,649 --> 00:18:45,001
I want to see him before I leave. Just
dropping me off near his condo is fine.

219
00:18:45,681 --> 00:18:48,229
Must be nice to have money.

220
00:18:51,472 --> 00:18:52,472
Hia.

221
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,272
Hia, dear.

222
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,200
Hia.

223
00:18:58,815 --> 00:18:59,815
Yes, dear?

224
00:19:04,548 --> 00:19:05,788
Take off your headphones first.

225
00:19:08,936 --> 00:19:11,529
I'm listening to an online sermon.
Can you call me in 10 minutes?

226
00:19:11,530 --> 00:19:14,018
Just talk to him, I won't interrupt.

227
00:19:14,019 --> 00:19:16,634
I don't want 10 minutes, I want it now.

228
00:19:16,635 --> 00:19:18,438
Take Aten to see Bom.

229
00:19:18,982 --> 00:19:20,502
They want to say their final goodbyes.

230
00:19:27,883 --> 00:19:28,883
Love...

231
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,200
The more you chase
it, the more it runs away.

232
00:19:32,067 --> 00:19:34,314
Try staying still and
broadening your horizons.

233
00:19:36,264 --> 00:19:38,907
And you'll find love all around you.

234
00:19:40,811 --> 00:19:43,091
The more love you give to this world...

235
00:19:44,587 --> 00:19:46,331
The more you'll get back.

236
00:19:54,537 --> 00:19:56,045
Your husband is so deep.

237
00:19:56,752 --> 00:19:57,861
Deep, my ass.

238
00:19:58,722 --> 00:20:00,917
He's just copying the
sermon and preaching to us.

239
00:20:01,824 --> 00:20:03,227
Should I say "Amen" to that?

240
00:20:04,406 --> 00:20:08,318
Up to you. I usually pay respect
to his chest before bed every night.

241
00:20:31,919 --> 00:20:33,424
P'Bom, you're back?

242
00:20:35,192 --> 00:20:36,192
Did I wake you up?

243
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:39,977
I was waiting for you, but I fell asleep.

244
00:20:41,111 --> 00:20:44,024
If you're tired, go back to sleep.
I'm going to shower.

245
00:20:44,885 --> 00:20:45,885
P'Bom.

246
00:20:47,424 --> 00:20:48,903
I went to see my dad today.

247
00:20:50,354 --> 00:20:52,913
I ordered someone to burn P'Erng's shop,
and half of it burned down.

248
00:20:52,914 --> 00:20:54,873
So Dad called me in to teach me a lesson.

249
00:20:57,820 --> 00:21:00,581
P'Erng's new boyfriend is the younger
brother of someone Dad respects.

250
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,982
What the hell did you do, Aten?

251
00:21:03,662 --> 00:21:05,362
When will you stop messing with Erng?

252
00:21:07,538 --> 00:21:08,698
Don't you even care about me?

253
00:21:10,374 --> 00:21:11,456
You never grow up.

254
00:21:11,457 --> 00:21:13,767
I've never grown up in
your eyes anyway, right?

255
00:21:15,535 --> 00:21:17,866
Dad ordered me to stay
away from you completely.

256
00:21:20,224 --> 00:21:23,986
Congratulations, P'Bom.
You don't have to suffer anymore.

257
00:21:23,987 --> 00:21:25,707
You don't have to break up with me anymore.

258
00:21:25,982 --> 00:21:28,337
And about P'Erng, I've cleared it up.

259
00:21:28,519 --> 00:21:29,722
It's all over.

260
00:21:30,266 --> 00:21:31,266
I'm not breaking up.

261
00:21:34,106 --> 00:21:36,516
When I wanted to break up,
you held onto me for dear life.

262
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:39,545
Now you're just going
to dump me this easily?

263
00:21:42,947 --> 00:21:46,045
