It hurt so damn much to watch.

530
00:40:55,650 --> 00:40:57,470
Because the one who made him cry

531
00:40:58,740 --> 00:40:59,740
wasn't me.

532
00:41:01,859 --> 00:41:03,667
At that moment, I swore to myself

533
00:41:05,662 --> 00:41:08,079
that I wouldn't let whoever
did this get away with it.

534
00:41:12,205 --> 00:41:14,134
When I found out it was Aten,

535
00:41:14,135 --> 00:41:15,197
I was angry,

536
00:41:16,149 --> 00:41:19,006
but deep down, I felt more
exhausted than anything.

537
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:23,497
It felt like everything was just
looping back to the same old story.

538
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:26,839
After the fire, Erng
went completely silent.

539
00:41:29,015 --> 00:41:31,596
No teasing, no arguing,

540
00:41:32,231 --> 00:41:33,834
not even a single insult directed at me.

541
00:41:35,104 --> 00:41:36,824
That's when I started to get really scared.

542
00:41:38,903 --> 00:41:41,675
But luckily, our home wasn't destroyed.

543
00:41:42,038 --> 00:41:43,454
The shop is still standing,

544
00:41:43,817 --> 00:41:45,252
and we're still alive.

545
00:41:46,386 --> 00:41:48,097
We just have to start rebuilding again.

546
00:41:49,457 --> 00:41:51,346
When Hia told me our home survived,

547
00:41:52,071 --> 00:41:53,710
I almost cried again.

548
00:41:54,481 --> 00:41:56,221
I don't know when it happened,

549
00:41:57,082 --> 00:41:58,461
but the word

550
00:41:59,322 --> 00:42:00,322
'shop'

551
00:42:01,217 --> 00:42:02,647
became 'home'.

552
00:42:03,735 --> 00:42:07,509
And the person beside me became family.

553
00:42:08,520 --> 00:42:12,422
Sometimes, I feel like I'm a jinx.

554
00:42:13,601 --> 00:42:17,338
Anyone who gets close
to me ends up suffering.

555
00:42:17,655 --> 00:42:20,468
But what made me angrier than the fire

556
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,679
was seeing Erng start to blame himself.

557
00:42:23,680 --> 00:42:26,079
I absolutely hate it
when he talks like that.

558
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:34,722
Being a good person and being the one
I love are two completely different things.

559
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:41,714
Even if Erng is stubborn, foul-mouthed,
and always looking for trouble,

560
00:42:45,659 --> 00:42:47,083
I'd still choose him anyway.

561
00:42:48,443 --> 00:42:51,666
At first, I thought I'd hate him so much.

562
00:42:52,845 --> 00:42:56,323
But seeing him cry, I just
felt sorry for him instead.

563
00:42:57,411 --> 00:43:01,054
Because in the end, Aten is just a kid

564
00:43:01,235 --> 00:43:04,123
who never got the love he actually needed.

565
00:43:05,393 --> 00:43:09,563
People who are truly happy
don't go around hurting others.

566
00:43:10,651 --> 00:43:13,759
The more he spoke, the more I realized

567
00:43:14,439 --> 00:43:16,415
how deeply unhappy Aten really was.

568
00:43:18,637 --> 00:43:21,135
Watching Erng talk to Aten surprised me.

569
00:43:21,452 --> 00:43:25,822
Despite everything he went
through, he still chose to forgive.

570
00:43:27,092 --> 00:43:30,390
Honestly, I'm not that strong.

571
00:43:31,297 --> 00:43:35,685
I just know that if we hold onto hatred,

572
00:43:36,184 --> 00:43:38,432
everyone's life will end up ruined.

573
00:43:38,931 --> 00:43:41,110
In the end, things wrapped
up in a pretty strange way.

574
00:43:42,380 --> 00:43:44,203
From almost killing each other,

575
00:43:45,382 --> 00:43:47,686
we ended up listening to
an online sermon together.

576
00:43:48,366 --> 00:43:50,796
Hia In always acts like a fake monk,

577
00:43:51,612 --> 00:43:52,613
but honestly,

578
00:43:53,112 --> 00:43:56,114
sometimes his words really do help people.

579
00:43:56,522 --> 00:44:01,046
After that, life slowly started
getting back to normal.

580
00:44:01,363 --> 00:44:04,635
I still get stressed and dream
about the fire sometimes,

581
00:44:06,539 --> 00:44:08,160
but whenever I'm with Hia,

582
00:44:08,931 --> 00:44:10,657
everything feels so much lighter.

583
00:44:11,972 --> 00:44:18,073
And of course, just as life starts to get
peaceful, Ong shows up to ruin it immediately.

584
00:44:19,479 --> 00:44:23,475
I'm starting to get used to
the chaotic life in this house.

585
00:44:23,792 --> 00:44:30,227
A house full of crazy, annoying,
and hopelessly romantic people.

586
00:44:30,520 --> 00:44:34,655
Seeing Erng talk to my mom felt so good.

587
00:44:37,103 --> 00:44:41,535
It feels like the person I love is truly
becoming a part of my family.

588
00:44:42,306 --> 00:44:45,414
I don't know what lies ahead,

589
00:44:45,958 --> 00:44:47,629
if the shop will ever be the same,

590
00:44:48,717 --> 00:44:50,761
or if the chaos is truly over.

591
00:44:51,033 --> 00:44:55,255
But right now, at least I know

592
00:44:55,844 --> 00:44:57,930
that no matter how many
times my world falls apart,

593
00:45:01,421 --> 00:45:03,667
I don't have to stand alone anymore.

594
00:45:04,160 --> 00:45:06,469
(Next Episode) Tomorrow, Erng and I
are going to the beach.

595
00:45:06,470 --> 00:45:08,290
A relationship-building trip.

596
00:45:09,040 --> 00:45:11,818
How does going to the
beach build a relationship?

597
00:45:11,819 --> 00:45:12,914
Well, it works.

598
00:45:13,141 --> 00:45:15,887
Erng and I fell in love
because of our trips.

599
00:45:16,386 --> 00:45:19,088
I also just found out that
Erng is protective of me too.

600
00:45:19,089 --> 00:45:21,909
Very, very protective.

601
00:45:21,910 --> 00:45:24,751
I have to wear a mermaid
tail for a photoshoot.

602
00:45:24,752 --> 00:45:26,813
Please be our photographer, Hia.

603
00:45:29,398 --> 00:45:32,165
It's time for me to return the favor.

